rechung und Literatur. Den Großkommentar benötigen Wirtschaftsprüfer, Steuer- und Unternehmensberater, vereidigte Buchprüfer, Rechtsanwälte, Richter.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAccountingxLaw and legislation. 4aBilanzrecht. 4aDeutschland. 7aLAW / Business & Financial.2bisacsh1 aUlmer, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA0 cprintz978311011947340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311087129640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110871296423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110871296/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014